{"word":"G2293 - θαρσέω - tharséō - thar-seh'-o - Be of good cheer","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θαρσέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tharséō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">thar-seh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be of good cheer</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - திடன்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"to be of good courage, be of good cheer"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2294 - θάρσος - thársos - thar'-sos/2294\">G2294</a>; to <i>have courage</i>: - be of good cheer (comfort). Compare <a href=\"#/G2292 - θαῤῥέω - tharrhéō - thar-hreh'-o/2292\">G2292</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2292/2292\">G2292</a>, <a href=\"#/G2293/2293\">G2293</a>"}]}